      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCd8b8daa029f610058c32ed44952c77d2"></a>Checking valve clearance
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1637"> </a>To check the valves clearance, it is necessary to have access to the cylinder head covers and then remove the components listed
            below.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1640"> </a>Remove both seats (<a href="77991.html#DUC7dd8e1d82a971005810ccc3160c450d2">Removing the seat</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1645"> </a>Remove the left and right-hand side instrument panel (<a href="77975.html#DUCc08298b82a73100585b0e07f17a720d2">Removing the panel</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1650"> </a>Remove the front half-fairing (<a href="77983.html#DUC6b420cf82a8210058217e66c96b901d2">Removing the front half-fairing</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1655"> </a>Remove the tank fairings (<a href="77987.html#DUC104f7d582a9610058109cc3160c450d2">Removing the tank fairings</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1660"> </a>Remove the fuel tank (Removing the fuel tank<a href="79858.html#DUC4747a3202b2310058d67a5fdf30dcfc4"></a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1664"> </a>Remove the filter box without disconnecting the throttle control cables and duly supporting it (<a href="79870.html#DUC50db19582b2310058d68a5fdf30dcfc4">Removing filter box and throttle body</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1669"> </a>Remove the coils.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1671"> </a>Undo the upper retaining screws of the timing belt covers (<a href="45036.html#DUC5af7ddf82516100581d2e6ffb59083d2">Removing the timing outer covers</a>).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1676"> </a>Remove the cylinder head covers (<a href="45072.html#DUC92cac200251a100584bad8c3784850d2">Removing the camshafts</a>).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1682"> </a>Undo the two retaining screws (1) of the centre cap (2) over the end of the crankshaft.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_4_006302782.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1687"> </a>Fit the tool handgrip (E) part no. <span class="bold">88713.0123</span> in the holes of the generator cover to be able to turn the crankshaft so that the valve on which the control is carried out
            is in rest position.
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_4_006402783.jpg"></center>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1695"> </a>With the valve in the rest position, slide a feeler gauge between rocker arm slider (A) and the lowest side of the cam (B)
            to measure the clearance.
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1697"> </a>The clearance must be within the specified limits:
         </div>
      </div>
      <table class="Format_A" width="100%" border="1">
         <thead valign="bottom">
            <tr valign="top">
               <th rowspan="1">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1708"> </a>Opening rocker arm
                  </div>
               </th>
               <th rowspan="1">&nbsp;</th>
            </tr>
         </thead>
         <tbody valign="top">
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" colspan="2" align="center" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1714"> </a>Intake
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1718"> </a>Operation
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1721"> </a>0.13 to 0.18&nbsp;mm
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1725"> </a>Checking clearance
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1728"> </a>0.10 to 0.25&nbsp;mm
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" colspan="2" align="center" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1732"> </a>Exhaust
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1736"> </a>Operation
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1739"> </a>0.13 to 0.18&nbsp;mm
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1743"> </a>Checking clearance
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1746"> </a>0.10 to 0.25&nbsp;mm
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
         </tbody>
      </table>
