      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1754"> </a>With the valve in the rest position, slide a feeler gauge between closing rocker arm slider (C) and the highest side of the
            cam (D) to&nbsp;measure the clearance.
         </div>
      </div>
      <table class="Format_A" width="100%" border="1">
         <thead valign="bottom">
            <tr valign="top">
               <th rowspan="1">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1765"> </a>Closing rocker arm
                  </div>
               </th>
               <th rowspan="1">&nbsp;</th>
            </tr>
         </thead>
         <tbody valign="top">
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" colspan="2" align="center" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1771"> </a>Intake
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1775"> </a>Operation
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1778"> </a> 0.05 to 0.10&nbsp;mm 
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1782"> </a>Checking clearance
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1785"> </a> 0.05 to 0.15 mm 
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" colspan="2" align="center" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1789"> </a>Exhaust
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1793"> </a>Operation
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1796"> </a> 0.05 to 0.10&nbsp;mm 
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1800"> </a>Checking clearance
                  </div>
               </td>
               <td rowspan="1" class="nocolsep">&nbsp;
                  <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e1803"> </a> 0.05 to 0.15 mm 
                  </div>
               </td>
            </tr>
         </tbody>
      </table>
